In terms of the beta diversity PCoA analyses, the two primer sets feature similar geometries of relatedness between sample sites within a dataset, with a cluster of similar sites on one end, and a spread of sites not closely similar to either each other or the main cluster on the other. However, the Uren data is more stochastic, with more outliers and greater distances from each other.

